#url = "https://turbo.ordinalswallet.com/inscriptions?offset=%s"
url = "https://turbo.ordinalswallet.com/inscriptions?offset=%s"
j = 0
while True:
    print("====", j, "====", len(inscriptions), url % j)
    r = requests.get(url % j)
    if r.status_code != 200:
        print("error", url % j, r.status_code)
        break
    data = r.json()
    for x in data:
        num = int(x["num"])
        inscriptions[num] = x
    print(num)
    if num < lowest_missing_id - 1000:
        break
    j+=len(data)
    
    #break

url = "http://ordinals.com/api/inscriptions/%"
while i < 200000:
    print("====", i, "====", len(inscriptions))
    r = requests.get(url % i)
    if r.status_code != 200:
        print("error", url % i, r.status_code)
        break
    data = r.json()
    for x in data["inscriptions"]:
        inscriptions[int(x["number"])] = x
    if data["next"] == None:
        break
    i = data["next"]
    #break

content_types = {}
for n,x in inscriptions.items():
    #print(x)
    ty = x["content_type"]
    if ty in content_types:
        content_types[ty] += 1
    else:
        content_types[ty] = 1

mimes = list(content_types.keys())
mimes.sort()
ctsorted = {i: content_types[i] for i in mimes}
content_types = ctsorted

# Filter ordinals for html projects that use window.location.href
url = "https://ordinals.com/inscription/%s"
for n,x in ords_content.items():
    if ("window.location.href" in x["data"].lower()):
        print(n, url % x["id"])
